  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "After updating the Node v17 Hardhat does not work properly. I've seen on StackOverflow others complaining about the same thing.\r\n\r\nReproduce:\r\n1. Use Node v17+\r\n2. Run `npx hardhat node`\r\n3. Get error message & failure:\r\n`Error HH604: Error running JSON-RPC server: error:0308010C:digital envelope routines::unsupported`\r\n\r\nI'm on Node v17.4.0\r\n\r\nWhat's the issue causing this?\r\n",
