    "body": "We only ensure compatibility for the latest three LTS versions of NodeJS - currently 12, 14 and 16. Any versions outside these three will not be guaranteed to work as there may exist breaking changes like the one you're experiencing. \r\n\r\nI would suggest using node version ^16.0.0 for your hardhat projects for now as I can't promise we'll be able to prioritize this refactor until node 18. ",
